The article is a presidential memorandum issued by Donald J. Trump on June 4, 2018. The memorandum delegates authority to the Secretary of State to submit a report required under section 709 of the Department of State Authorities Act, Fiscal Year 2017. The Secretary of State is to consult with the Secretary of the Treasury, the Attorney General, and the Director of National Intelligence in preparing the report. The memorandum also states that this delegation of authority applies to any future public law that is the same or similar to section 709. Finally, the memorandum instructs the Secretary of State to publish the memorandum in the Federal Register.